For the most common questions (after sending the request)
What is the next step after sending the request?
When the customer sends the order, the store will be notified. The store will verify the availability of the order data and can approve it or reject it, and the customer will be notified accordingly.
If it means the stroe approves my order?
When the store approves the customers request, this means that the store is ready to carry out the request and agrees to communicate with the customer about the request.
What should I contact the store?
How will I contact the store if my order is approved?
When the store accepts the customers request, the request will appear on the customers orders page, the customer can contact the store at that time.
You have chosen to pay when ordering the product. When should I pay?
Payment will be made after the store approves the request with all its details, and the payment will be through a production application.
When I choose to pay on demand, do I have to transfer the amount to the store directly?
The payment process will be in a production application, and the amount will not go directly to the store until you confirm that the product has been received with the full order details.
You have chosen to pay on delivery. How do I pay?
Payment will be made upon receipt to the store owner directly, and my production will continue to be verified.
